<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/22076509">《金陵十三钗》中，十二名妓女为了救女学生而替其赴局，这是一种怎样的精神？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1011418" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"></div>


